            <p class="para">Per ulteriori informazioni, consultare il <a href="http://rubyonrails.org/" class="ulink" title="http://rubyonrails.org/">sito web di Ruby on Rails</a>.</p>
          </li>
<li class="list itemizedlist">
            <p class="para">Anche <a href="http://pragprog.com/titles/rails3/agile-web-development-with-rails-third-edition" class="ulink" title="http://pragprog.com/titles/rails3/agile-web-development-with-rails-third-edition">Agile Development with Rails</a> è un'ottima risorsa.</p>
          </li>
<li class="list itemizedlist">
